<template>

import FormRadioFieldNames from './FormRadioFieldNames.vue'

export default {
  components: {
    BRow,
    BCol,
    FormRadioBasic,
    FormRadioCustom,
    FormRadioColor,
    FormRadioContextualStates,
    FormRadioStackInline,

    FormRadioFieldNames,
  },
}
</script>
